Miss Dalton, we're just security.

96
00:11:35,327 --> 00:11:37,887
Well, my colleague was murdered,

97
00:11:37,963 --> 00:11:40,932
brutally, from what I've been able
to piece together.

98
00:11:41,967 --> 00:11:46,267
