182
00:18:26,138 --> 00:18:28,402
I like it. It suits you.

183
00:18:29,074 --> 00:18:30,268
Oh, thanks.

184
00:18:41,954 --> 00:18:42,943
Shit.

185
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,252
