200
00:19:48,820 --> 00:19:51,789
and now there's some
creepy bio-culture growing out of her nose.

201
00:19:51,857 --> 00:19:53,620
No, no, she's fine.

202
00:19:55,127 --> 00:19:56,526
Everything's fine.

203
00:19:58,163 --> 00:19:59,994
